            Interview Tracker!
          </blockquote>
          <br />
          <cite
            ><img src="img/customer-1.jpg" alt="Cutomer-1" /> Spiderman
            Chauhan</cite
          >
        </div>
        <div class="col span-1-of-3 go">
          <blockquote>
            By going through the solutions even without trying is not a good
            idea. You should take your own time to try and solve the problems by
            yourself. Even if it takes more than an hour for a 'hard' problem,
            you keep trying
          </blockquote>
          <br />
          <cite><img src="img/customer-2.jpg" alt="Cutomer-2" /> Karen</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="col span-1-of-3 go">
          <blockquote>
            Interview Tracker is a great platform to polish your programming
            skills and prepare yourself for software engineering interviews.
            With questions around data structures, algorithms and systems
            design.
          </blockquote>
          <br />
          <cite
            ><img src="img/customer-3.jpg" alt="Cutomer-3" /> Homer
            Simpson</cite
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

